longBusinessSummary: Manomay Tex India Limited manufactures and sells denims and denim fabrics in India. The company exports its products to Colombia, Mexico, Egypt, Chile, Venezuela, Paraguay, Guatemala, Peru, Ecuador, Lebanon, Sri Lanka, Bangladesh, Argentina, and Bolivia. Manomay Tex India Limited was founded in 1978 and is based in Bhilwara, India.
